{"tid":2396300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「貧困戶」家中藏茅台等貴價酒　內地官方親民騷被質疑造假　網民喊話：我家都要臨時走訪","createTime":"2021-02-05T13:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T13:27:15.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e36307018784053281b7d4051e7d8efab195652f","tid":2396300,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vPhejNNUQ9UbiVZdZFlbU5TiU2I=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZBAXHHGUGJCBFAAI6N6ETEBQUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvPhejNNUQ9UbiVZdZFlbU5TiU2I%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZBAXHHGUGJCBFAAI6N6ETEBQUU.jpg&h=ea39715d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山東青島市的街道官員探訪困難戶，網民卻發現該貧困戶家中擺放茅台等貴價酒。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_cqPxYue5t1zoIEUaYz5N1WUPpo=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BM26A3HAANCWZALZAJVPU4VTBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_cqPxYue5t1zoIEUaYz5N1WUPpo%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBM26A3HAANCWZALZAJVPU4VTBI.jpg&h=ab41f668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民放大照片一看，質疑困難戶家中出現疑似跑步機或按摩器。但官方指，其實是嬰兒車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VyRXOizsLfk4Cv7NenoonZjqV1U=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2S2YYXDUCRGYFPK6XL5DOXJYFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVyRXOizsLfk4Cv7NenoonZjqV1U%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2S2YYXDUCRGYFPK6XL5DOXJYFI.jpg&h=70676399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民發現屋內有平面電視機，懷疑該困難戶其實並不算貧困。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n事發於本周三（3日），青島市城陽區棘洪灘街道辦微信公眾號，發佈了一篇題為《春節走訪困難戶濃濃溫情暖人心》的文章，當中的一幅配圖顯示，被走訪慰問的困難戶家的書架上，擺放了茅台、五糧液等價酒樽。不少網民質疑該「困難戶」是臨時演員，並非真的困難戶，其中可能存在舞弊現象。<br />\n<br />\n有指，臨近農曆新年，價格較便宜的茅台酒每瓶近1,500元，但因求過於供，近日已被炒至3,100元。<br />\n<br />\n由於網民討論得沸沸揚揚，城陽區棘洪灘街道辦昨日下午再度通過微信公眾號發佈一則《情況說明》，表示引起今次爭議的配圖中，貴價酒樽其實是空酒樽，是該困難戶參加親友宴會時，將客人喝剩的酒樽帶回家中收藏。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210205/ISM3CQ2FUFA5VDVGUS4SGB7VRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210205%2FISM3CQ2FUFA5VDVGUS4SGB7VRE%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=3db30efa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210205%2FISM3CQ2FUFA5VDVGUS4SGB7VRE%2F&h=a2768c0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210205/ISM3CQ2FUFA5VDVGUS4SGB7VRE/</a>"},{"pid":"7f92bc0d7b8f8852565f5e618c0a3e3fd1630b3f","tid":2396300,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"高官： 我家裏面這些錢都是假的 這些女人都是朋友來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6838c6d2708cc3a99fec577c0cf0941740615628","tid":2396300,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"假酒大把啦"},{"pid":"f346f672976abfca7a6f69a9de2d89a18001490c","tid":2396300,"uid":194588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6838c6d2708cc3a99fec577c0cf0941740615628","tid":2396300,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"假酒大把啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"假酒先千五<br />\n真酒你估千五會唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fedfa94311857be5cfad6bdd6a747d1eba8fab","tid":2396300,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"